                        "if(HullSpecial(Player()) == FindBonusByNameInCfg('Keller_Newlomatelebala') && Int_for_Keller_Krinator == 2) {",
                        "  DChange(106);",
                        "  exit;",
                        "}"
                    ],
                    "#": 519,
